verbose_text: To prove that the deletion in dNulp1 was responsible for the lethal phenotype of dNulp1 1 # mutants, we determined whether the lethality of dNulp1 1 # could be rescued by over-expressing UAS-dNulp1-PA using the ubiquitous Arm-Gal4 driver.
evidence: dNulp1 1#  could be rescued by over-expressing UAS-dNulp1-PA using the ubiquitous Arm-Gal4
